    ],
    "faq": [
      {
        "question": "Is SPARC methodology compatible with existing development workflows?",
        "answer": "Yes, SPARC integrates with existing workflows through Claude Code's Task tool and MCP coordination, enhancing rather than replacing current practices."
      },
      {
        "question": "What are the limits on concurrent agents?",
        "answer": "SPARC supports up to 20 concurrent agents with adaptive scaling based on workload complexity and system resources."
      },
      {
        "question": "How does SPARC integrate with version control systems?",
        "answer": "SPARC includes GitHub integration modes for PR management, code review, and repository analysis with automated workflow triggers."
      },
      {
        "question": "Is my code and data safe when using multi-agent orchestration?",
        "answer": "Yes, all operations run locally with optional cloud features. Memory persistence uses encrypted storage with configurable TTL."
      },
